78e99e705db51ca84cb9972cc6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"540\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-alt=\"An image shows a specific location on a map on the left and a screenshot of the game on the right.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe third wolf statue is all the way at the other side of the level, right before you reach the second Ancestral Heart. Clear out the enemies herefor the barrier around the wolf statue to disappear. Once all the demons are defeated, just throw your shield at the wolf statue.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"h1117935\"\u003e\u003ca id=\"jewel\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003eGrabbing the jewel\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter shattering all three wolf statues, the barrier surrounding the Sorcerer statue will disappear. You can then interact with the statue and grab the Wraithstone, which can be \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/doom-the-dark-ages-upgrades-shotgun-flail-pulverizer-1851780282\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/doom-the-dark-ages-upgrades-shotgun-flail-pulverizer-1851780282\"\u003eused to upgrade\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e your weapons, shield, and melee capabilities\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/games/doom-the-dark-ages\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/doom-the-dark-ages\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eDoom: The Dark Ages\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, be sure to \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/new-doom-dark-ages-review-is-it-good-xbox-ps5-game-pass-1851779839\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}